		•	Emotions section with EmotionSelector (required)
		•	Note field with textarea (optional)
		•	People tags section with TagInput (optional)
		•	Context tags section with TagInput (optional)
		•	Save and Cancel buttons
	•	Create mode:
		•	Form fields are empty on mount
		•	Stores are loaded if needed (emotions, tags)
		•	Save creates new log via emotionLogStore.createLog()
		•	Validation: at least one emotion required
	•	Edit mode:
		•	Log data is loaded and pre-populated on mount
		•	Save updates log via emotionLogStore.updateLog()
		•	Validation: at least one emotion required
