⸻

Out of Scope

	•	Advanced editor features (rich text, formatting, attachments)
	•	Emotion statistics or analytics (this will come in Profile view later)
	•	Bulk operations (bulk edit, bulk delete)
	•	E2E tests (comprehensive testing comes in Story 12)
	•	Advanced validation (e.g., checking if emotion IDs exist in store)
	•	Tag management UI (viewing all tags, editing tag names) – this will come in a later epic
	•	Filtering or querying logs by emotion, date, or tags (this will come in Profile view later)
	•	Export or share functionality
	•	Undo/redo functionality
	•	Auto-save functionality
	•	Keyboard shortcuts

