	•	All components created in previous stories will continue to work after Story 11
	•	Story 11 is purely additive (adds new editor view) and doesn't modify existing functionality
	•	No inconsistencies detected that would require backtracking from Story 10 or earlier stories

21.	Top App Bar Title:
	•	The epic mentions: "Title such as 'Log emotion' or 'Edit log' (depending on mode)"
	•	However, we will keep the default title "Mindful Growth" for consistency with JournalEditorView
	•	AppTopAppBar shows "Mindful Growth" as the default title for all views
	•	This is an intentional design decision – custom titles are not needed for Story 11
