22.	Route Naming Convention:
	•	Story 11 uses route names: 'emotions-edit' and 'emotions-edit-id'
	•	This follows the same convention as journal routes: 'journal-edit' and 'journal-edit-id'
	•	No inconsistency – route naming is consistent

